thread.title: BRIEF-SQS: Assystem Services Deutschland Intends To Initiate Compulsory Acquisition Proceeding

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-SQS: Assystem Services Deutschland Intends To Initiate Compulsory Acquisition Proceeding

organizations.name: assystem services deutschland intends to initiate compulsory acquisition proceeding feb

text:
Feb 5 (Reuters) - SQS Software Quality Systems AG:
* ASSYSTEM SERVICES DEUTSCHLAND GMBH INFORMED SQS THAT IT HAS RECEIVED VALID ACCEPTANCES IN RESPECT OF 96.16 PERCENT
* ASSYSTEM SERVICES DEUTSCHLAND GOT VALID ACCEPTANCES IN RESPECT OF 96.16 PERCENT OF SHARES/DEPOSITARY INTERESTS IN SQS
* ASSYSTEM SERVICES DEUTSCHLAND INTENDS TO INITIATE A COMPULSORY ACQUISITION PROCEEDING Source text - bit.ly/2nCYiHt Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
